Sentencas: The area specific polarization resistance of symmetrical cells was studied to analyze the electrochemical behavior of the LBCO nanostructures as cathodes for Solid-Oxide Fuel Cells.
Titulo: Nanostructured La0.5Ba0.5CoO3 as cathode for solid oxide fuel cells
